Lights and screens @linksmultimedia.ng

This event was very special to us at blue velvet, it allowed for us to be expressive in our design and execution. Prepping for months and so much anxiety leading up to the day of the event. 

This is our highest luxury package which is a custom made event as everything  was built from scratch for the event. 
Planning and prepping for this event took 4months 

So thankful for the team members on board this project. It was a MAJOR production. 

Thanking God for helping us pull through, awesome bv staff who showed complete dedication in executing all the designs and to @linksmultimedia.ng and @theconcertweddings for working with us on this project and doing far beyond their job description on this event to make sure everything came together beautifully. There is power in collaboration. 

Stage and platform design @theconcertweddings
